1. download scalapack
down linux version for general machine. 

1.1 enter BLAC directory

make

2. make

cp SLmake.inc.example SLmake.inc

3. install blas and lapack

```
sudo apt-get install libblas-dev liblapack-dev
```

if you want to compile blas by yourself.

download blas-linux.tar.gz

cp Bmake.inc from Bmake/Bmake.inc-linux
pay attention, edit Bmake.inc:

1. g77 maybe doesn't work. change g77 to gfortran.

2. setting mpich lib, if you use apt install mpich,then be careful this part
```
   MPIdir = /usr/include/mpich
   MPILIBdir = /usr/lib/mpich/lib
   MPIINCdir = $(MPIdir)
   MPILIB = $(MPILIBdir)/libmpich.a
```


4. make

make exe

make example

5. check 
enter to example
mpirun -np 4 ./xcscaex
